                                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[The iPhone Air Is Missing One 5G Feature, and You’d Probably Never Notice]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/the-iphone-air-is-missing-one-5g-feature-and-youd-probably-never-notice/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Tim Brookes]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/iphone-air.jpg" length="179" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Iphone]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple iPhone Air]]></category><category><![CDATA[5g]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Small phone, tiny problem.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Apple’s brand new slim iPhone is official in the form of the iPhone Air. Pretty much every detail was leaked prior to the big event, including the name. One thing that wasn’t really spoken about, however, was 5G performance.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 10 Sep 2025 18:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/the-iphone-air-is-missing-one-5g-feature-and-youd-probably-never-notice/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Apple Just Made the iPhone 16 a Worse Deal]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/apple-just-made-the-iphone-16-a-worse-deal/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Arol Wright]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/iphone-16-cover-image-1.png" length="3410" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Iphone]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple iPhone 16]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Don't buy it. At least not from Apple.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>The iPhone 17 range was announced yesterday, and it's a pretty different lineup to anything we've seen before. And Apple really wants you to buy it. So much so that it has not only discontinued the iPhone 16 Pro range, but it has also nerfed the regular iPhone 16 phones, too.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 10 Sep 2025 17:39:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/apple-just-made-the-iphone-16-a-worse-deal/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[AI Slop Has Shattered My Trust in Google Pixel Phones]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/ai-slop-has-shattered-my-trust-in-google-pixel-phones/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Bertel King]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/robot_hands_reaching_for_a_google_pixel_smartphone_surrounded_by_red_warning_icons_with_exclamation_marks.png" length="1289" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Android]]></category><category><![CDATA[Android Phones & Tablets]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google Pixel]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google Pixel 10]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Pixels are hardly the only phones with AI, but they're the most aggressive. 
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>I have long not been a Google guy, but I still considered Pixel phones to be devices I could easily recommend to others. Google's approach to AI has changed that. I no longer feel comfortable using or recommending these phones.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 10 Sep 2025 17:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/ai-slop-has-shattered-my-trust-in-google-pixel-phones/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Get Half off This Moto Watch Fit Smartwatch]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/get-half-off-this-moto-watch-fit-smartwatch/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jorge A. Aguilar]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/motorola-moto-watch-fit-being-worn-by-woman-on-green-background.jpg" length="251" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Android]]></category><category><![CDATA[Smart Watches]]></category><category><![CDATA[Deals]]></category><description><![CDATA[
